Milanka Brooks https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Milanka_Brooks 0 Milanka Brooks is a British actress from London, England, best known for playing Ionela in Benidorm in 2015-2016. Brooks also played Elena Tulaska in "USS Callister", a 2017 episode of Black Mirror.
